```html
@media (min-width: 20rem) {
    body::after {
        content: "Splus";
        font-size: 0;
    }
}
@media (min-width: 47.5rem) {
    body::after {
        content: "Mplus";
        font-size: 0;
    }
}
@media (min-width: 62.5rem) {
    body::after {
        content: "Lplus";
        font-size: 0;
    }
}
```

